      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8045659150639517358, guid: fbcc40e91526859428bab09db558e208, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_value.<Text>k__BackingField
      value: '[focused] One of my most memorable quests was the defeat of a formidable
        band of marauding raiders. [excitedly] We ambushed them at dawn, fighting
        fiercely to protect our village. [determined] I led my men into the fray,
        our swords clashing amidst the chaos. [reflective] That day, I learned the
        true meaning of courage and the importance of brotherhood in arms.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
